'''Jai''' was a [[Dathomirian/Legends|Dathomiri]] word for [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]. According to the legends of the [[Witches of Dathomir]], a Jai was a powerful [[Gender/Legends|male]] witch from [[The galaxy/Legends|the stars]].

